Grammar

    0 $accept: program "end file"

    1 program: constdecls forstatement

    2 constdecls: constdecls constdecl
    3           | ε

    4 constdecl: type id ASSIGN intlit SEMICOL
    5          | NOPT type id ASSIGN intlit SEMICOL
    6          | type id ASSIGN LCURLY intlist RCURLY SEMICOL

    7 intlist: intlit COMMA intlist
    8        | intlit
    9        | ε

   10 forstatement: FOR LPAREN constdecl expr SEMICOL unarystmt RPAREN LCURLY forstatement RCURLY
   11             | FOR LPAREN constdecl expr SEMICOL unarystmt RPAREN LCURLY outstatements RCURLY

   12 outstatements: outstatements outstatement
   13              | outstatement

   14 outstatement: OUT ASSIGN expr SEMICOL

   15 type: INT

   16 expr: expr CROSS expr
   17     | expr LESS expr
   18     | expr STAR expr
   19     | expr MINUS expr
   20     | term

   21 unarystmt: loc POSTINC

   22 term: factor
   23     | LPAREN expr RPAREN

   24 factor: intlit
   25       | loc

   26 intlit: INTLITERAL

   27 loc: id
   28    | id LBRACKET id RBRACKET

   29 id: ID


